						<div class="postbody">Agreed, there is a hard limit to how many bytes of data can change between frames.  But what I find fascinating is all that this community has been able to do in those few small bytes.  I was thinking today about the perceived &quot;Full Motion Video&quot; limit and how you could use midframe and vblank bankswithing to pull it off.  You couldn't maintain it for an long time, but it's do able.</div>

