						<div class="postbody">Good brain dump.  Many thanks. I'd planned on a similar outline but got to work on my anologies and storytelling to smooth it out some.<br /><br />For example, the 60fps is true but since there is not a standard definition of a &quot;frame&quot; it's better to think about it in terms of bandwidth and windows of opportunity (Hblank/Vblank).  I probably won't get into the technical intricacies of the $2000/2005/2006 headaches in details.  Probably just a heads up when discussing the registers.</div>

